{"tid":479278,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貼大字報　拆橫額　東華補選爆火藥味 - 李八方","createTime":"2017-11-25T02:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T07:28:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"022e9711b0c0d59a0c04e6824286f1c07c13add5","tid":479278,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:55:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171125/[url]20225177[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171125%2F%5Burl%5D20225177%5B%2Furl%5D&d=KAbvVb99HXKgOeR6UCIXGIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=8ec8101b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171125%2F%5Burl%5D20225177%5B%2Furl%5D&h=99dc2873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171125/[url]20225177[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n貼大字報　拆橫額　東華補選爆火藥味 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n   <br />\n<br />\n      <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171125/large/a1305a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171125%2Flarge%2Fa1305a.gif&h=0abbc47f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日就係中西區區議會補選日，東華選區選情好激烈，建制派支持嘅呂錦強同民主黨嘅伍凱欣由頭鬥到尾，噚日兩大陣營仲各自報警，話俾人選舉抹黑同攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n噚日區內呂錦強宣傳單張及橫額上，俾人貼咗好多小單張，話佢搵另一候選人劉舒燕𠝹票，亦有一啲係針對佢個人嘅抹黑，而呂就喺fb話由補選開始至今，佢不斷喺網上被人攻擊及抹黑，選舉宣傳品噚日仲俾人惡意破壞同抹黑，由於事態嚴重，佢同助選團已經報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n不過伍姑娘都投訴，佢話喺般含道麗怡大廈對面嘅橫額，全部俾人拆走晒，有部份仲俾人丟棄在附近山坡，所以佢同助選團亦已經報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n警方初步調查後認為係刑事毀壞，佢亦不點名回應咗嗰啲抹黑呂嘅單張，話呢啲標語同海報影響公平選舉，佢哋亦有再到警署報案，又譴責呢類破壞行為，希望選舉能夠喺公平公正情況下舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171125/large/a1305b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171125%2Flarge%2Fa1305b.gif&h=8434c39c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d073fe9f48cd5f548ed362eb9aa6bc34f2cb847","tid":479278,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"唉，大家都係建制派，有咩咪唔啱講到啱，做乜又報警又抹黑係到內訌呢？！"}]}